OL,3,CDuffy recounts kidnapping and sexual
OL,4,Cassault in new Disney+ documentary
OL,6,FWelsh singer Duffy will feature in a
OL,7,Fnew documentary recounting her rise to
OL,8,Ffame and subsequent kidnapping and
OL,9,Fsexual assault for the first time.
OL,11,FThe 41-year-old, known for the songs
OL,12,FMercy and Warwick Avenue, will open up
OL,13,Fabout her life and time away from the
OL,14,Fpublic eye in a new Disney+ feature-
OL,15,Flength documentary.
OL,17,FThe star, whose real name is Aimee
OL,18,FAnne Duffy, shot to fame in the late
OL,19,F2000s following the release of her
OL,20,Fdebut album Rockferry.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
