OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774552271
OL,3,CDuffy recounts kidnapping and sexual
OL,4,Cassault in new Disney+ documentary
OL,6,FHer best-known hit single from this
OL,7,Frecord, Mercy, was a UK number one for
OL,8,Ffive weeks in 2008, and propelled the
OL,9,Fsinger to international success.
OL,11,FShe went on to release a second album,
OL,12,FEndlessly, in 2010 before withdrawing
OL,13,Ffrom the public eye. The singer
OL,14,Frevealed nearly a decade later that
OL,15,Fshe had been drugged, raped and held
OL,16,Fcaptive.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
