OL,3,CDuffy recounts kidnapping and sexual
OL,4,Cassault in new Disney+ documentary
OL,6,FThe new documentary will chronicle the
OL,7,Fsinger's life, from her upbringing in
OL,8,FWales to her music career to the
OL,9,Fpresent, nearly 15 years after she was
OL,10,Fattacked.
OL,12,FThe film will also include interviews
OL,13,Fwith the singer's family, friends, and
OL,14,Fclose peers in the music industry.
OL,16,FDirector Gill Callan said: "Duffy's
OL,17,Flife has been shaped by success and
OL,18,Ffame, but equally by pain, defiance,
OL,19,Fand an irrepressible sense of self.
OL,26,@xD@\OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
