OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774552271
OL,3,CDuffy recounts kidnapping and sexual
OL,4,Cassault in new Disney+ documentary
OL,6,F"I'm drawn to the tension between
OL,7,Fvulnerability and confidence in her
OL,8,Fstory and how a person can be deeply
OL,9,Faffected by their experiences, yet
OL,10,Fstill find a powerful, expressive
OL,11,Fvoice that is unmistakably hers."
OL,13,FSean Doyle, vice president of
OL,14,Funscripted at Disney+, added: "This
OL,15,Ffilm will give Duffy the chance to
OL,16,Ftell her story in her own words.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@aO]vD@_OU
