OL,3,CDuffy recounts kidnapping and sexual
OL,4,Cassault in new Disney+ documentary
OL,6,F"We set out in a search for impactful,
OL,7,Ffemale-led stories in collaboration
OL,8,Fwith Northern Ireland Screen, and it's
OL,9,Fa privilege that Duffy's is the first
OL,10,Fwe're able to help tell. But above
OL,11,Fall, I'm especially in awe of Duffy `
OL,12,Ffor her honesty and courage to share
OL,13,Fher story."
OL,15,FDuffy's debut album Rockferry went on
OL,16,Fto win the Grammy award for best pop
OL,17,Fvocal album in 2009 along with three
OL,18,FBrit awards including best British
OL,19,Ffemale, British breakthrough act and
OL,20,FBritish album.
