OL,3,CDuffy recounts kidnapping and sexual
OL,4,Cassault in new Disney+ documentary
OL,6,FIn 2010 she released her album
OL,7,FEndlessly, featuring the song Well
OL,8,FWell Well, which peaked at number nine
OL,9,Fin the UK album charts.
OL,11,FDuring the Covid-19 pandemic in 2020,
OL,12,FDuffy shared a song titled Something
OL,13,FBeautiful with BBC Radio 2, however,
OL,14,Fthe track was never officially
OL,15,Freleased.
